settings.heading: Can I install your wallpaper in the bathroom?
settings.row_content: Our wallpapers can absolutely be used in a bathroom but some ventilation in the space (a window or vent) is preferred, and it would be a good idea to talk to your wallpaper installer about double-pasting the corners for extra insurance against humidity.
